00:56:01,543 --> 00:56:04,812
"Sewaktu kita bertengkar dan kamu sakit"

883
00:56:05,543 --> 00:56:09,113
"Kamu ke kamar mandi dan mengeluarkan suara"

884
00:56:10,782 --> 00:56:13,653
"Boom, boom, boom"

885
00:56:17,523 --> 00:56:20,693
"Semuanya baik-baik saja"

886
00:56:21,532 --> 00:56:25,062
"Tapi kenapa kamu sangat membencinya hari itu?"

887
00:56:26,803 --> 00:56:29,642
"Boom, boom, boom"

